Description: Pass PostHog MCP server to sandbox agent sessions.

The sandbox environment provides POSTHOG_MCP_URL, POSTHOG_PERSONAL_API_KEY,
and POSTHOG_PROJECT_ID. The agent-server reads these and constructs an MCP
server config that is passed to the Claude session via the ACP newSession call.

This patch should be applied to the @posthog/agent package in the PostHog/twig repo.

